{
  "text": "Furthermore, it has been suggested that accessibility to health care, measured by lower availability of mammography facilities, and/or primary care physicians-delays the detection of early stage breast cancer [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
